  <brief_title>A Randomized Trial of Vitamin D to Reduce Respiratory Infection</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Vitamin D3 Supplementation to Reduce Respiratory Infections in Children and Adolescents in Vietnam: A Blinded, Placebo-controlled Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
